PIERRE AIRLINES — PASSENGER COMPENSATION POLICY
================================================

EU REGULATION 261/2004 — FLIGHT DELAY COMPENSATION

Delays of 2-3 hours:
- Right to meals and refreshments
- Two free phone calls or emails

Delays of 3+ hours on flights under 1500km:
- €250 compensation per passenger
- Right to meals and refreshments

Delays of 3+ hours on flights 1500km-3500km:
- €400 compensation per passenger
- Right to meals and refreshments

Delays of 3+ hours on flights over 3500km:
- €600 compensation per passenger
- Right to meals and refreshments

Delays of 5+ hours:
- Full refund of ticket if you choose not to travel
- Return flight to original departure airport if applicable

CANCELLATIONS:
- Less than 14 days notice: same compensation as delays above
- Alternative flight offered within 2 hours: compensation halved
- Extraordinary circumstances (weather, strike): no compensation owed

PIERRE AIRLINES GOODWILL POLICY (above EU law):
- Any delay over 1 hour: 500 Pierre Miles credited automatically
- Any delay over 3 hours: lounge access voucher issued
- Any cancellation: double miles on next booking